claims.claim_content:
A flight plan analysis method that determines a flight plan decision regarding a proposed flight plan for an unmanned aerial vehicle (UAV) (102), the flight plan analysis method comprising: storing risk factor data in a flight plan database (108);
communicatively coupling a flight plan analysis unit (106) to the flight plan database (108);
receiving, by the flight plan analysis unit (106), a proposed flight plan for the UAV (102);
analyzing, by the flight plan analysis unit (106), the proposed flight plan and the risk factor data; and
determining, by the flight plan analysis unit (106), the flight plan decision based on the analyzing.

